        <odd id="ref10">
            <head>Early American History Note</head>
            <p>These two volumes contain musical scores compiled by Franklin Peale, son of Charles Willson Peale, and his wife in 1823. The lyrics of the songs may be of interest to folklorists and cultural historians.</p>
        </odd>
