        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Benjamin Franklin Peale was a son of Charles Willson Peale, and a naturalist, paleontologist, and traveler. He was elected to the American Philosophical Society in 1833.</p>
